overview: The story revolves around a student in the medical school who lives with a scientist who invented a chemical compound that makes him invisible. A single person is in love. Salwa is also the same, but her father rejects a single medical student and prefers marrying his daughter from Taher. It is clear that Tahir is a human being who is just and honest in his life, as is clear to him. One of these chemicals uses this chemical powder to reach his beloved Salwa.
title: من اين لك هذا
